column34: Recently, actor Johnny Depp lost his libel case as the judge sided with his ex-wife, actress Amber Heard. There was clear evidence that Amber Heard was the abuser in the relationship, where as Depp was incriminated without full proof, he should be innocent until proven guilty. Because of the results, Warner Bros. Company forced Johnny out of his role of Grindelwald in the upcoming trilogy movie of the franchise "Fantastic Beast and Where to Find Them" However, his Ex Amber Heard is still able to reprise her role in the upcoming "Aquaman 2", How is this fair? I'm asking for your support to either get Johnny's role and reputation back, or have it equal and get Amber Heard kicked from her role as well. #JusticeForJohnnyDeppÂ
